                  <p><strong>Primary:</strong> Infiltrate a Soviet psychiatric hospital, locate a political prisoner, and escape with him across hostile territory.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="analysis-panel verdict" data-label="CONTEXT">
                  <p>Working alongside Pete Thornton, MacGyver must navigate Soviet security, Soviet vehicles, and surveillance systems. The mission requires precision timing, mechanical sabotage, and practical field engineering to create escape routes and disable pursuit.</p>
